    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2232870/extras/a63ee3f908ca592fba19235ccecf06eb.poster.avif?t=1726312434\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2232870/extras/a63ee3f908ca592fba19235ccecf06eb.webm?t=1726312434\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2232870/extras/a63ee3f908ca592fba19235ccecf06eb.mp4?t=1726312434\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>The Backrooms Origins is a first person exploration and psychological horror game about famous internet creepypasta the backrooms. <br><br>Play VHS tapes and learn more about origins of the backrooms. Experience the infinite liminal spaces and try to escape this terrifying and dangerous complex.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2232870/extras/27f7563c7345fc07efbb36222380f863.poster.avif?t=1726312434\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2232870/extras/27f7563c7345fc07efbb36222380f863.webm?t=1726312434\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2232870/extras/27f7563c7345fc07efbb36222380f863.mp4?t=1726312434\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Play the VHS tapes which is recorded by a scientist of Supernova Research Facility. Explore the levels of backrooms and learn how everything is started. <br><br>Enter this uncharted universe and explore the worlds of full of unknowns and dangers.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2232870/extras/135a2a72b6dd0dc38b4f827ae44ab2a7.poster.avif?t=1726312434\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2232870/extras/135a2a72b6dd0dc38b4f827ae44ab2a7.webm?t=1726312434\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2232870/extras/135a2a72b6dd0dc38b4f827ae44ab2a7.mp4?t=1726312434\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Feel the fear in it's most realistic way with realistic VHS graphics and terrifying ambiance. Experience the horror with first person gameplay.</strong>",
